| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4217 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4a3874a7-e3db-513c-8f6b-e0cf0967ea55"
